  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>Data Element: PERSON RELATIONSHIP (MAIN CARER) - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
  <div>
      <p>
         <xref outputclass="element" keyref="element_person_relationship__main_carer_">PERSON RELATIONSHIP (MAIN CARER)</xref>
 is the same as attribute 
              <xref outputclass="attribute"
               keyref="attribute_relationship_to_person_for_community">RELATIONSHIP TO PERSON FOR COMMUNITY</xref>.         </p>
      <p>
         <xref outputclass="element" keyref="element_person_relationship__main_carer_">PERSON RELATIONSHIP (MAIN CARER)</xref>
 is the relationship between the 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
 and the 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_person">PERSON</xref>
 who undertakes the main caring role for them.        </p>
      <p>
For specific National Code usage , see 
              <xref outputclass="attribute"
               keyref="attribute_relationship_to_person_for_community">RELATIONSHIP TO PERSON FOR COMMUNITY</xref>.        </p>
  </div>
